Text: Thanks very much for the uploads, but I notice the past few months of Billboard are dated incorrectly. The torrent title says 4-21 but the description and the issue uploaded are 4-27. As a result a couple of issues I think are 1-26, 3-9, do you by any chance have them or know which torrents those issues are? I checked them all and can't find them. thanks!
